ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of SHAMSHUDDIN ALIDINA of Markham, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of 10 months or a period expiring on the day prior to the coming into force of the Balance Refugee Reform Act, whichever periods ends earlier, effective May 4, 2012.
